Today I was at chris' house.  At first I was having fun, but then we started to play super smash bothers meele for game cube. I was teamed up with michael and chris and harrison were on a team.  I had eight lives left when michael died.  Harrison and Chris had only three or four each.  They told michael to start stealing my lives to come back to life and then comit suicide so that they i would go down to one life.  I eventually got them down to one life as well.  Then I died.  I got pissed because they gave my controller to someone else when they cheated and i would have won.  They started to tell me to stop being such a sore loser.  As well as the fact that just the turn before, Chris was mad because he said i was being cheap.  Well, what i was doing was nothing compared to how cheap he was being,  they were then making fun of me and kept bragging about how they always won.                             
Earlier that day i had to tell harrison to say thanx for me disigning his computer.  Then i gave him a really nice sound card and he didnt say thanx even though it was like four hours after i made him say thanx for the computer.  I feel like he only calls me over when he needs something, never to hang out.  He has so far only called me for the computer, he called me this morning for it.  The other night he invited michael and chris to a sleepover, and i only found out cause i heard them talking about it at the pool.  Then Chris asks me to come and suddenly Harrison cant have one at his house, but he could if it was at chris' house, but he couldn't either.  So we dicided to have one at  my  house the next day.  Only Harrison cant sleepover at anyones house anymore, even though it was the exact same night he could sleep over at chris'.  Maybe im beying paranoyd but i dont really think he likes me.  He seems to call everyone else in the neighboorhood but me and that makes me mad.  Anyways, it felt pretty good to get that off my chest.  Ill talk to u guys another time.
